Man I can't explain how much obsessed I am with this song.
This duo is just heavenly, it felt like a dream come true after listening to Kaavish and Abdul Hannan together.
Abdul Hannan with his angelic voice and the sensational lyrics,
and then the legendary Kaavish with his deep sorrowful voice which hides so much pain, some of which is expressed by his words.
Just Astonishing, thank you Coke Studio, for this collab🥺❤‍🩹
